      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled solver with documented unit tests and regression suite covering all hemolysis-relevant modules.",
      "rationale": "Solver is version-controlled and has a regression suite, but unit-test coverage of the hemolysis transport module is incomplete and no independent code audit has been performed, yielding achieved level below required."
