      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation experiments conducted on the same pump geometry and operating envelope as the intended VAD deployment conditions.",
      "rationale": "Validation was performed on the FDA generic pump geometry at nominal design point only; off-design and patient-specific flow conditions relevant to VAD use were not included in the validation matrix."
