      "acceptanceCriteria": "Systematic evaluation of turbulence model and hemolysis constitutive law uncertainty via multiple model forms with documented selection rationale.",
      "rationale": "Only the SST k-omega turbulence model was used; no alternative turbulence models or hemolysis law variants were evaluated, leaving model-form uncertainty unquantified."
